'From Squeak3.2gamma of 5 February 2002 [latest update: #4839] on 22 April 2002 at 3:10:44 pm'!"Change Set:		slotInfoFix-swDate:			22 April 2002Author:			Scott WallaceA workaround for another annoying issue arising when trying to use projects in a meanstream Squeak image that were created with the now-very-ancient plug-in image"!!SlotInformation methodsFor: 'access' stamp: 'sw 4/22/2002 15:10'!type	"Answer the type of the receiver, initializing it to Number if it is nil"	type isEmptyOrNil ifTrue: [^ type _ #Number].	type first isUppercase ifFalse: [^ type _ type capitalized].		"because of lingering, annoying issue of projects created in a plug-in image"	^ type! !